LICENSE NOTICE – MUNICIPAL INFORMATION MODEL (GGM)
Copyright © 2025 Municipality of Delft
https://github.com/Gemeente-Delft/Gemeentelijk-Gegevensmodel

The Gemeentelijk Gegevensmodel (GGM) is an information model developed by the Municipality of Delft. It aims to support semantic interoperability and data exchange within and between Dutch municipalities.

This work includes:
- semantic models in UML, JSON, and other formal representations;
- accompanying documentation, illustrations, and explanatory content.

LICENSE TERMS

1. The core information model (UML files/repositories, JSON schemas, tables and definitions) is licensed under the:

    **European Union Public Licence (EUPL), version 1.2**

    You are free to use, modify and redistribute this work, provided that derivative works are shared under the EUPL or a compatible license.
    Full license text: https://joinup.ec.europa.eu/collection/eupl/eupl-text-eupl-12

2. Visual elements (such as figures, diagrams and explanatory documentation) are licensed under the:

    **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY 4.0)**

